                    The content on this website is not intended to substitute for professional advice, whether religious, legal, medical, financial, or psychological. You should always consult a qualified professional in the relevant field before making any decisions based on the information provided here. Any reliance on the information is at your own risk.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Educational and Cultural Nature of Content</h2>
