                <p class="mb-6">
                    All content on the site is protected by copyright. Personal, non-commercial use is permitted with attribution to the source. Any other use requires prior written permission.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Consent to Terms</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">
                    By using this website, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to this disclaimer.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Updates</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">
                    We reserve the right to modify or update this page at any time without prior notice. Periodic review is recommended.
                </p>

                <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    Last updated: December 23, 2025
                </p>
            </>
        )}
    </section>
</Layout>